    "en": {
      "title": "Murder after rape of an elderly woman who lived alone",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kankesanthurai - An elderly woman who was living alone at home in Kollangalatti has been murdered after being brutally raped, police said.",
        "An elderly woman, Thavamani (age 78), was found dead with cuts on her neck on Friday morning.",
        "Following this, the body of the grandmother was autopsied in the presence of the forensic officer of the Jaffna Teaching Hospital.",
        "Police said the suspect would be arrested soon as evidence became available. (R)"
      ],
